732
01:25:58,843 --> 01:25:59,773
Abang?

733
01:26:00,803 --> 01:26:04,083
Adakah awak pasti tentang tempat ini?

734
01:26:04,083 --> 01:26:05,483
Aduhai!

735
01:26:05,483 --> 01:26:06,933
Berhenti tanya saya.

736
01:26:06,933 --> 01:26:10,053
Kenapa ada peti simpanan di sini?

737
